result: War Until The Philosophy Which Hold One Race Superior And Another Lower Is Finally And Permanently Discredited And Abandoned, Everywhere Is War - Me Say War. That Until There Is In Longer First Class And Second Class Citizen Of Any Nation, Until The Color Of A Man's Skin Is Of No More Significance Than The Color Of His Eyes - Me Say War.
